Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.94,0:03:00.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.45,0:03:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You are the mushi-shi, Ginko-san, you said?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.89,0:03:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.18,0:03:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Shirasawa, the village head.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.13,0:03:12.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I asked you to come on behalf of the village.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.76,0:03:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, our village lies deep in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.25,0:03:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a quiet village where even\N the wind doesn't pass through.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Especially on snowy nights like tonight, sometimes there is not a single sound,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and even chattering voices are said to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.13,0:03:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And on those nights,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.98,0:03:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,some villagers contract an ear illness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.58,0:03:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are both ears affected?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.41,0:03:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Almost all the cases involve only one ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The disease has left doctors in the town,\N scratching their heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.48,0:03:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought it might be an out of \Nthe ordinary influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.73,0:04:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed... this mucus...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.41,0:04:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The cause is... mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.93,0:04:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.35,0:04:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called {\i1}Un{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:14.54,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs150\c&H191B19&\3c&H191B19&\blur1\move(928,534,928,610,21,1481)}Un
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.85,0:04:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The {\i1}Un{\i0} is eating the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.34,0:04:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Normally, the {\i1}Un{\i0} inhabit the forest,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.08,0:04:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,but snow absorbs sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.49,0:04:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I think they've come down to the village in search of sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.51,0:04:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... here they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.99,0:04:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Quite a large colony has made a nest here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder they are devouring all the sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They then leave the colony and become a parasite in a living host.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.74,0:04:56.34,Default,,0,0,0,,At a glance, it looks like a snail.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,They disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They just moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.18,0:05:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know there is an organ in the ear which looks just like a snail?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.99,0:05:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The hungry {\i1}Un{\i0} abandons its shell, \Nsettles in there as a parasite,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:16.71,Default,,0,0,0,,then eats all the incoming sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.03,0:05:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,However, that doesn't mean that the organ is damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.18,0:05:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.91,0:05:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's the hot water you asked for. Is this enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.63,0:05:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.85,0:05:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If I pour this into the ear...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.07,0:05:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,See? It's gone now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.42,0:05:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Salty! What the heck is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.22,0:05:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Salt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.92,0:05:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Salt?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! I can hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.06,0:06:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Now if you just spray that salt \Nwater around under the roof,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,that should solve your problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.90,0:06:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the first time I've seen a mushi-shi at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.40,0:06:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,There is still one other who has\N caught illness in both ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.68,0:06:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.66,0:06:30.87,Default,,0,0,0,,His symptoms are markedly different from the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.69,0:06:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I ask that you not let the others in the village know about his condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.61,0:06:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.73,0:07:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.82,0:07:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Maho.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been like this since last winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.10,0:07:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,When those horns suddenly appeared,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.59,0:07:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He stopped hearing the sounds he could hear before
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and began hearing sounds that he'd never heard before.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.90,0:07:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Even on a silent night like this, \Nhe can hear sounds from all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Whispering sounds, roaring sounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.26,0:07:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't go away no matter if he covers his ears, or drowns out everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.02,0:07:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He says the noises still enter through his horns.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.55,0:07:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This could be a case of {\i1}Ah{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.85,0:07:53.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.03,0:07:59.75,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fs100\c&H161E1F&\3c&H161E1F&\blur1\frz19.36\frx2\fry6\move(812,272,812,578,21,6736)}Ah
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.74,0:07:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,They are mushi which co-exist with {\i1}Un,{\i0} \Nand eat the silence which the {\i1}Un{\i0} generate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.37,0:08:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If one is infected with {\i1}Ah,{\i0} one loses the ability to recognize noises close to them,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,because the {\i1}Ah{\i0} take in sounds \Nfrom all over indiscriminately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.75,0:08:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But compared to {\i1}Un{\i0}, they are very few in number.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.90,0:08:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,There is only one other recorded case of a patient being treated for {\i1}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,According to that document,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.77,0:08:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,even though the same salt-water\N treatment for {\i1}Un{\i0} was used,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,the {\i1}Ah{\i0} could not be extracted from the ear.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.35,0:08:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, various herbal medicines were tried,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but none of them were successful.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.63,0:08:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end of the winter after the\N onset of the patient's illness,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.74,0:08:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,due to the noises that came to her day in and day out like a flood,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.46,0:08:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,her spirit became exhausted and eventually...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.58,0:08:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,she became so weak that she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end of... the following winter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.29,0:09:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, first we should get to know our enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.26,0:09:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear my voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.83,0:09:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.38,0:09:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The noises that surround me have quieted down a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.05,0:09:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you came,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.13,0:09:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,the noises got louder and louder.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.57,0:09:32.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought my head would split open.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.29,0:09:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.72,0:09:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a tendency to call out mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.25,0:09:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Mushi are noisy creatures, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I used this smoke to keep them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.47,0:09:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Mushi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.85,0:09:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that what I'm hearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where most of your \Nnoise is probably coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.60,0:09:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Humans have particularly bad hearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.44,0:09:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The majority of animals hear \Nmany more noises than we do.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.84,0:10:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But they say that there's still a spectrum of loud noises that even animals can't hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.72,0:10:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the spectrum of the voices of mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.97,0:10:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do mushi speak this loud?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.02,0:10:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.63,0:10:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Each mushi's murmur is probably very minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:22.12,Default,,0,0,0,,But there are countless numbers of mushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.12,0:10:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What would happen if so many of them murmur a word?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.19,0:10:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that, like a loud echo, \Nthose murmurs act in concert,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.72,0:10:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,and that sound is reverberating throughout the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.41,0:10:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The mushi called {\i1}Ah,{\i0} which is existing deep in your ears, eats your silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.65,0:10:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, your horns sprouted and...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.62,0:10:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,noises from a wide variety of spectrum started flowing in through them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.33,0:10:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.93,0:10:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I didn't see anything wrong with your ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:55.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you tell me how those horns appeared?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.22,0:11:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I was covering my ears with my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.51,0:11:06.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Last winter,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.69,0:11:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,my mom died...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.23,0:11:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,She often covered her ears,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.92,0:11:17.99,Default,,0,0,0,,so I remembered that and tried to do the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.93,0:11:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Horns sprouted from my forehead.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Your mom was... covering her ears?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.90,0:11:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would she do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.55,0:11:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.51,0:11:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom had the same illness as me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.30,0:11:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,she had horns, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So she shouldn't have been able to stop the noises even though holding ears.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.22,0:11:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My mom said something to me then,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and with her weakened hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.01,0:11:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,she covered my ears firmly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.31,0:12:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I ought to remember what she told me then...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and I always try to recall what she said,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,but the sounds keep rushing into\N my head and I can't hear her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.99,0:12:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although I feel bad for him, it's fortunate...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that there was a previous case\N in the exact same environment.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The key to treatment must lie somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.54,0:12:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The last days of my daughter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She was to be pitied.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:51.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She could not sleep because of the noises.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.35,0:12:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,She never mentioned this in front of Maho...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.09,0:12:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...but she would constantly say...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.10,0:13:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want to get a good sleep in a place...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.06,0:13:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,850)}{\i1}where no noise will reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.19,0:13:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And, just like the case you mentioned earlier,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,at the end of the following winter after her symptoms first occurred,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.99,0:13:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,she finally went to that place where she longed to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So she suffered until the end?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.67,0:13:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.12,0:13:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.55,0:13:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.34,0:13:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,One day my daughter suddenly said...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.30,0:13:33.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mom... the sounds went away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.57,0:13:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Now I hear nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.65,0:13:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1975)}{\i1}I miss the noises that I so feared.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.77,0:13:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,And then, soon after,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.77,0:13:55.43,Default,,0,0,0,,as if fading away, she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.87,0:14:00.58,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying she couldn't hear anything right before she died?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.58,0:14:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.79,0:14:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything else you recall?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No. But, I'm afraid the story Maho told you earlier occurred around that time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.06,0:14:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,At that time, I did think it was strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.17,0:14:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I wondered for what reason my daughter did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.61,0:14:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The silence that she experienced right before death...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.04,0:14:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Did the Ah leave her body, realizing that its host was about to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.07,0:14:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it did, then her hearing \Nwould've gone back to normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.99,0:14:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Why wasn't she able to hear anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.39,0:14:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And what was she trying so hard to stop from hearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.48,0:14:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Where do you think you're going?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.04,0:14:49.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Then again, he probably can't hear me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.28,0:14:52.39,Default,,0,0,0,,D...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.73,0:14:58.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just... going out for a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell Grandma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.19,0:15:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If I just stay inside the house, I'll go even crazier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I keep thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.74,0:15:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep thinking of when mom died, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.98,0:15:26.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.54,0:15:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}After all, he watched his mother \Ndie of the same illness he has.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.47,0:15:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's starting to snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.16,0:15:43.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I shouldn't have let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Maho...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.08,0:15:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Maho?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.45,0:15:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Ginko-san, I can't find Maho.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.85,0:15:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw which direction he went.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.93,0:15:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why didn't you stop him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.05,0:15:58.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.62,0:16:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But that doesn't mean sound is absent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.32,0:16:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If you listen carefully,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.35,0:16:16.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}even snow falling can make a sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.26,0:16:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If sound is absent around you,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.61,0:16:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then you can hear the beating of your heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.43,0:16:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if you pick up various sounds,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.03,0:16:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I guess you're then unable to hear individual sounds...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.18,0:16:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that became extreme,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}then perhaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.58,0:16:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}{\i1}Perhaps that's what she meant when she said that all the sounds went away?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.55,0:17:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I really was planning to go home right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.42,0:17:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But it started to snow hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.82,0:17:14.39,Default,,0,0,0,,so... I decided to wait here until it stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But instead, it started to snow harder and...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Huh? What happened to his voice?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.08,0:17:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.97,0:17:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop fighting over me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.88,0:17:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one of you is the {\i1}Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.34,0:17:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Un{\i0} is coiled clockwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.04,0:17:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ah{\i0} is coiled counterclockwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.17,0:17:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You must be {\i1}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.40,0:18:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Maho, give me your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.31,0:18:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Place them on my ears like your mom did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It dissolved!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.92,0:18:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you cover your ears with both hands,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.84,0:18:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,all is still not silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:52.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Your daughter was not trying to keep noises out right before she died,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.52,0:18:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but rather, I think she was trying to listen to the sounds she could hear at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.45,0:19:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear a little noise like the rumbling of the earth...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They say that is the sound made by the movement of your arm muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:13.83,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, I think the {\i1}Ah's{\i0} weakness is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the noise that other creatures make as they live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.52,0:19:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,However, if the Ah were to live as a parasite in a living creature's body,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.24,0:19:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,that sound would always be \Nechoing within the host's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.06,0:19:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Living inside a host could not be\N a comfortable place for {\i1}Ah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:29.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why it tries to erase the body's sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.45,0:19:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Either the Ah dissolves, or the host\N gets weakened and dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.70,0:19:40.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That one year is probably the time required for the answer to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.86,0:19:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I think your daughter realized that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.90,0:19:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But, by that time, she was too weak,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.87,0:19:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and it was too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.01,0:19:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Maho...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.02,0:19:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,...can you hear it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.89,0:20:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This is my sound.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.69,0:20:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Long ago, I saw it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.22,0:20:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,with your father...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.58,0:20:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,A mountain that spewed fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.06,0:20:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This sound is exactly like the sound of lava.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.31,0:20:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why, when I feel uneasy to the point of wanting to disappear,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.84,0:20:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I listen to that sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A sound like lava, which can make anything melt...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.01,0:20:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like it can melt everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.41,0:20:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,all the uneasiness and hardship.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Come now, you try it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.67,0:20:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,3900)}You have lava flowing within you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The lava...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.52,0:21:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Maho...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.93,0:21:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The red hot lava...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.19,0:21:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,...is flowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.35,0:21:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take these as my fee then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.90,0:21:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.10,0:21:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But are you sure it's enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.25,0:21:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.31,0:21:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay with that, Maho?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.73,0:21:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the world quiet, Maho?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.98,0:21:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll take a while to get used to it,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.34,0:21:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,and you'll crave for the world you just parted with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.36,0:22:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,But when spring comes and it gets lively around here, you'll forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't... forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.81,0:22:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I was listening to it this whole time...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.75,0:22:14.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the same sound Mom was listening to.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.66,0:22:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pretty sound...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.17,0:22:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,3800)}...enough to give you the chills.
